\subsubsection{Maybe and related}

A version of \texttt{fromJust}
that gives a more helpful error message.
\begin{code}
getJust :: String -> Maybe t -> t
getJust _   (Just x)  =  x
getJust msg Nothing   =  error msg
\end{code}

